# Large hero video — exceeds GitHub 100MB limit. Host on a CDN / Git LFS, or compress.
public/BrabusIslandVilla_H264_WEB.mp4

# Secrets — never commit. Vite inlines every VITE_ var into the public bundle,
# so a real secret must never carry that prefix in the first place.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Vercel
.vercel

# NOTE: public/renders/gen/ is generated by `npm run images` but IS committed
# on purpose. Media.jsx emits <source srcset> pointing at those files, and once
# a browser picks a <source> a 404 renders a BROKEN image — it does not fall
# back to the <img> JPEG. Ignoring them would blank every render on the live
# site the moment a deploy did not run the (cwebp/avifenc-dependent) generator.
